<br>
In exp group just about any hybrid will do fine.<br>
<br>
I seriously doubt warriors can solo better than sk, rangers and paladins and even bards.<br>
<br>
Another thing is that warriors are just about the worst taunter in the game, actually scratch that they are.<br>
I got all respect for your tanking skills, but often you are not tanking because that hybrid just out taunted you.<br>
<br>
In pog raids my sk tanks a fair bit vs the other 5+ warriors, mainly cause even if i dont use spells my mace and shield just own the average warriors wepon taunt, sometimes i even wish i had evade because my wepon procs (vampric embrace) and taunts back over.<br>
On an average pog raid the only warriors who do the main tankeing own Epics, the rest, i would say 1/10 have the wepons to keep agro.<br>
<br>
But to be honest i forgot what the topic was about, i seem to remember it being the best tank, and warriors are the best eqpic mob tank, but probably draw with hybrids situational because of variouse skills.<br>
<br>
Often the warriors is not the best tank.. mainly because they cant keep agro, and if they cant keep agro they are not tanking, and if they are not tanking, if they are not tanking then they are not the best.<br>
<br>
Paladins/SK have genrallys the same AC as warriors at later lvs, paladins with there buffs, and sk with there own unique buffs that stack with every other AC buff, add that to shields and marginaly AC loss items compared to the warriors ones and actually SK/PAl have more AC than warriors. <br>
What they dont get is DISCS wich is the only thing that makes them tank better, Hybrid HP are not off by that much and there AC is not to far.. warriors are ment to tank VIA skill not items, and your discs are what make you good.<br>
<br>
Also note that defensive is going to be your main disc for tanking.. every warrior i see use offence dies on raids, because they want that last rush of glory, prey you got somone who cant tank till that heal hits you. (wich actualy is my main job, taunt from the warriors who use offence and get there ass kicked)<br>
<br>
Warriors are good, i playe many of them.. but they do get boaring.. i would play another warrior with a strong bunch of friends, as that passes the time rather well but they did get extreemly boaring when no groups are around. Also bear in mind just about any class solos better than the warrior, but warriors do well with partners so 2 man groups are rather viable.<br>
<br>
